{"tid":473193,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"呢幾年既智能電話推出，都好似唔係好震撼咁","createTime":"2017-11-19T04:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T17:32:45.000Z","uid":19275,"like":84,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"4027bd0b469d382614601400fd8bdb8dbc4be033","tid":473193,"uid":19275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"係個世界要求高左，定喺啲大公司真係技窮？<br />\n依家講緊iPhone 8/X呢啲旗艦機都唔係好俾到驚喜人，想舊電耐用啲就又要省電模式又點點點，成萬銀買部電話翻黎淨係打下機咁樣，旗艦機黎嫁喎，淨係打下機玩下whatsapp嗰啲舊電先熬到一日都叫旗艦機？<br />\n<br />\n另外，當年multi touch, FaceTime, Touch ID,Siri 每樣出黎嗰時其實都好震撼，今次face id其實個技術都真係好高，點解就硬係無乜感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990dcf329e0ef81f164ea6b5d6612450b9d8c49b","tid":473193,"uid":19275,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"以前靠jailbreak得翻黎既成功感，依家係靠維修電話先得到翻黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感覺自己唔只係一般用家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14569d0316faa0a14f0499043b62c14fa7dc8deb","tid":473193,"uid":6083,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"整個立體投射好唔好？ <br />\n好似starwars咁"},{"pid":"a50edf8bbf90795cd967519a9f40f0ef1f05ef12","tid":473193,"uid":107436,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:18:03.000Z","msg":"其實除左faceid都冇咩其他新野出，反而mon大左要係咁用gesture我覺得offset番佢既好處，其他尻野唔講（autocorrection), 換個mon換粒U其實係使用上既改進都唔大，遲早都會慢<br />\n<br />\nAndroid d機起碼肯開個nfc比人用,  仲有發展既潛質"},{"pid":"e50b90eeca94c6a344a0b1401360dae30e6d6559","tid":473193,"uid":124107,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c5556df87223aa156e9b32d9cfa3841c012ab30","tid":473193,"uid":85659,"like":29,"dislike":5,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"老